<p>Next her husband is seen on the sofa again where he is rubbing his wife's feet. 'Hmmm, interesting,' he says after she conveys the conversation.</p>

<p>He then goes on to say she needs to tell her mother explicitly that she is being cut off. 'You need to cut her off now,' says her spouse pointing his finger for emphasis.</p>

