<p>Tough lady: Then the clip turns to Ashley all made up with a green cage lace dress on in her living room. She says, 'I think I handled it pretty well. I think I was tough - tough love'</p>

<p>This comes after she shocked fans by sharing that she and her husband have had 'threesomes.'</p>

